trans-unit.resname: The International Institute of Technology and Management (IITG) is a private institution of Higher Education. Founded in September 2022 by two partners, the institute is aligned with the guidelines of sub-regional university institutions, as well as national and international standards relating to Higher Education.
trans-unit.source: The International Institute of Technology and Management (IITG) is a private institution of Higher Education. Founded in September 2022 by two partners, the institute is aligned with the guidelines of sub-regional university institutions, as well as national and international standards relating to Higher Education.
trans-unit.target: L'IITG est un établissement privé d’Enseignement Supérieur. Fondé en septembre 2022 par des partenaires Gabonais et étrangers, l’institut s’arrime aux Directives des institutions sous régionales universitaires, ainsi qu’aux normes nationales et internationales relatives à l’Enseignement Supérieur.Il comprend un conseil de direction et un conseil académique issues de sa gouvernance académique.

trans-unit.resname: IITG is committed to developing in learners educational and professional ethics, critical thinking, analytical and problem-solving skills, creativity, innovation and leadership.
trans-unit.source: IITG is committed to developing in learners educational and professional ethics, critical thinking, analytical and problem-solving skills, creativity, innovation and leadership.
trans-unit.target: IITG se donne pour mission principale de contribuer au développement d’une société tournée essentiellement vers la Compétence et la Connaissance. Ainsi, les formations professionnelles et innovantes qu’il proposées visent à rendre les apprenants compétitifs, dans un univers de plus en plus globalisant
